data.description: ONCE-IN-A-LIFETIME OPPORTUNITY, come look quickly! Sellers remodeled to make this their dream home, then life circumstances changed.  This is your chance to purchase a home REMODELED TO PERFECTION at a BARGAIN PRICE!  (This is NOT a flip.). **Main floor Primary Suite.** Hardwood floors through-out main and second level. **Walls, ceilings, trim, doors (interior and exterior), spindles, stair railing ALL freshly painted, no surface left untouched.** Luxurious Primary Suite w/new Barn Doors added between Bathroom and Bedroom, new Bathroom fixtures, new Bathroom white six-panel closet doors, new Bedroom remote ceiling fan, so much new!  Sparkling updated Kitchen w/quartz countertops, SS appliances, lots of storage.  **ALL appliances stay.**.  New light fixtures and light switch plates throughout main and second floor.  New carpet runner added to stairs. Finished spacious Lower Level with tall ceilings.  *Beautiful treed view from back, heated neighborhood pool.*. Nothing to do but move in and live in luxury! ASSUMABLE LOAN at 6.875%, 30 year-fixed. Note: Patio is being replaced and Deck repaired by HOA in Spring 2024.
